/target
**/*.rs.bk
Cargo.lock.orig

# The repo-root .gitignore excludes *.der, but these certificate fixtures are
# committed on purpose -- they are load-bearing include_bytes! inputs for tests.
!crates/revenant-core/src/pki/testdata/*.der
# Bundled, shipped trust anchors (not test data) -- also load-bearing.
!crates/revenant-core/src/config/anchors/*.der
